“Kaizen” is a Japanese term that captures the concept
of continuously making many small improvements

***************
Run SonarQube in Docker (Local)
***************

docker run -d --name sonarqube \
  -p 9000:9000 \
  sonarqube:lts-community

***************
Run Sonar Scanner on your Spring Boot project
***************

mvn sonar:sonar \
  -Dsonar.projectKey=my-spring-app \
  -Dsonar.host.url=http://localhost:9000 \
  -Dsonar.login=your_token_here

